  "description": "<p><strong>🌟 Job Highlights:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Master a variety of<strong> beauty devices</strong></li>\n  <li>Learn how to <strong>connect with clients confidently</strong> and professionally</li>\n  <li>Get hands-on with <strong>slimming procedures using advanced machines</strong></li>\n  <li>Build meaningful relationships with clients to <strong>encourage loyalty and long-term results</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>💰 What You’ll Get:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Attractive Commission Package</strong> – Your effort = your reward</li>\n  <li>🗓️ <strong>Up to 7 Days Off Per Month</strong></li>\n  <li>🚫 <strong>No Overtime Required</strong></li>\n  <li>🚇 <strong>4 Outlets Conveniently Located Near MRT Stations</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>🙌 What We’re Looking For:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Experience in the beauty, wellness, or slimming industry</li>\n  <li>A customer-first mindset, positive attitude, and a can-do spirit</li>\n  <li>Someone who takes initiative and genuinely enjoys helping others look and feel their best</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you're passionate about wellness and ready to grow your skills in a fun, supportive environment, we’d love to have you on our team!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><em><strong>Please note: </strong></em><em>The job title and salary range etc indicated are for reference purposes only. The final offer may differ based on experience, qualifications, and internal evaluation.</em></p>",
